higher asset integrity.        </div>        <table width=\"100%\">          <tbody>\n<tr>            <td width=\"33%\" style=\"padding:0 10px 0 0;\">              <div style=\"background-color:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:16px;border-radius:12px;\">                <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#0f172a;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 6px 0;\">Animations</div>                <div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:650;color:#0f172a;margin:0 0 6px 0;\">Precise animation transfer</div>                <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#475569;line-height:1.65;\">                  Preserve timing and motion curves for keyframed and procedural animation workflows.                </div>              </div>            </td>            <td width=\"33%\" style=\"padding:0 5px;\">              <div style=\"background-color:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:16px;border-radius:12px;\">                <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#0f172a;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 6px 0;\">3D Models & Materials</div>                <div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:650;color:#0f172a;margin:0 0 6px 0;\">Geometry & shading, intact</div>                <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#475569;line-height:1.65;\">                  Import native geometry faithfully, with support for standard and Redshift (RS) materials.                </div>              </div>            </td>            <td width=\"33%\" style=\"padding:0 0 0 10px;\">              <div style=\"background-color:#f8fafc;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:16px;border-radius:12px;\">                <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#0f172a;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 6px 0;\">Characters & Splines</div>                <div style=\"font-size:14px;font-weight:650;color:#0f172a;margin:0 0 6px 0;\">Rigged assets & curves</div>                <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#475569;line-height:1.65;\">                  Bring in rigged characters plus splines/curves for modeling, MoGraph, and animation use.                </div>              </div>            </td>          </tr>        </tbody>\n</table>      </td>    </tr>        <tr>      <td style=\"padding:26px 28px;border-top:1px solid #e5e7eb;background-color:#ffffff;\">        <div style=\"font-size:11px;letter-spacing:1.2px;color:#16a34a;margin:0 0 8px 0;\">Customer Reviews</div>        <div style=\"font-size:24px;font-weight:750;color:#0f172a;margin:0 0 10px 0;\">What our customers say</div>        <div style=\"font-size:14px;color:#475569;margin:0 0 18px 0;line-height:1.75;\">          Real feedback from artists and studios using this addon in production.        </div>        <table width=\"100%\">          <tbody>\n<tr>            <td width=\"33%\" style=\"padding:0 10px 0 0;\">              <div style=\"background-color:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:16px;border-radius:12px;\">                <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#d6a44a;margin:0 0 8px 0;letter-spacing:0.5px;\">★★★★★</div>                <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#475569;line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 12px 0;\">                  “This addon has completely transformed my workflow. Importing C4D files directly into Blender is a game-changer.”                </div>                <div style=\"border-top:1px solid #eef2f7;padding-top:12px;\">                  <div style=\"font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a;margin:0 0 2px 0;\">Alex C.</div>                  <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#64748b;margin:0;\">3D Artist</div>                </div>              </div>            </td>            <td width=\"33%\" style=\"padding:0 5px;\">              <div style=\"background-color:#ffffff;border:1px solid #e5e7eb;padding:16px;border-radius:12px;\">                <div style=\"font-size:12px;color:#d6a44a;margin:0 0 8px 0;letter-spacing:0.5px;\">★★★★★</div>                <div style=\"font-size:13px;color:#475569;line-height:1.75;font-style:italic;margin:0 0 12px 0;\">                  “Perfect for our pipeline. We